title: Sam Altman (Open AI): The Future of AI Research from DALL·E to GPT-3
description:
Sam Altman, Co-Founder, and CEO of Open AI joins Scale AI CEO Alexandr Wang in a fireside chat during Transform 2021 Conference. The two discuss Open AI’s latest research from DALLE to GPT-3 and discuss AI research broadly.

OpenAI - https://openai.com/
